            <title>[CASSANDRA-17675] Revert the removal and deprecate withBufferSizeInMB(int size) in favor of the new withBufferSizeInMiB(int size)</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-17675</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;withBufferSizeInMB(int size)&lt;/em&gt; was renamed in 4.1.&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The right way to do it was to deprecate it and add the new one &lt;em&gt;withBufferSizeInMiB(int size)&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Add back &lt;em&gt;withBufferSizeInMB(int size)&lt;/em&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
